						<span class="tags">Tagged with <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/pentagon/" rel="tag">pentagon</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/syria/" rel="tag">Syria</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/us/" rel="tag">US</a>, <a href="http://blog.mktgeist.com/tag/war/" rel="tag">War</a></span>					</p>
